<p>A minor addendum, since a semi-major update has been made. There are now links to the canon IRC chatroom (#Apotheosis) and <a href="http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/collab:3law">brainstorming sandbox</a> in the contributing tab, as well as a module to display a <em>complete</em> listing of all works within this canon (as it is mainly tales that are linked on the main tab, and not all goi formats and skips are linked in the info tabs). This list is <em>not</em> in chronological order, and is instead sorted by rating. Additionally, blurbs for three GOIs were added to the paratech trade tab last month, something which went unannounced at the time.</p>

