<p>Yet another update, this one a bit more substantial. Changes enumerated below:</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Yeah,&nbsp;this&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;long&nbsp;list</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Told&nbsp;ya&nbsp;so</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>Added skips and goi formats to the home tab</li>
<li>Added blurbs to all articles on the home tab</li>
<li>Folded the Successors tab into the Prometheus Labs tab</li>
<li>Retitled the Paratech Trade tab to Other Organizations</li>
<li>Cut the publications list from the References tab</li>
<li>Added a list of major characters to the References tab</li>
<li>Massively expanded the glossary</li>
<li>Moved all the separate lists of paratech to a single list in the References tab</li>
<li>Pruned the locations list</li>
<li>Removed Wondertainment from the GOI list for the time being</li>
<li>Added ICSUT and Black Queen to the GOI list</li>
<li>Reorganized the GOI list a little bit</li>
<li>Added a bit of CSS to increase the spacing of lists</li>
<li>Updated the Contributing tab to reflect these changes</li>
<li>Removed the complete list of stuffs from the contributing tab</li>
<li>Expanded the suggested reading a bit</li>
<li>Probably other stuff I forgot</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Thanks to Conwell, A Random Day, TyGently, and Aiden Eldritch for their assistance in getting the update done.</p>

