														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2573804">
									

<p>There's nothing stopping you from using things from this canon outside of Third Law. Many people have used the magic system that Clef outlined for the GOC canon, but few of those articles are actually in the GOC canon. Heck, people have already used things from Third Law outside of Third Law, like Conwell's use of Three Portlands in <a href="/austringers">Austringers</a>. In fact, I actively encourage people to do this kind of stuff, as it leads to all sorts of wonderful and creative stories that wouldn't or couldn't exist within the confines of Third Law.</p>
<p>TL;DR: Third Law isn't some kind of exclusive clubhouse for these ideas or characters, feel free to use Third Law stuff outside of Third Law.</p>

